        <abstract> 
<p>Sends new edition of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. Has made some corrections.</p> 
            <p>Has been led into dreadful blunder on p. 75 by erroneous calculations of a mathematical friend.</p> 
<p>Opposes change of <hi rend="italic">Entstehung</hi> into <hi rend="italic">Ursprung</hi> [in title] even if more correct. It would make readers think it is a new book.</p> 
        </abstract>
