            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6774.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from J. V. Carus, 3 June 1869</ref> and n. 2. CD refers to the fifth edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin.</hi></note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See letter from Ponderer to the <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>, [before 5 June 1869], and letter to the <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>, 19 June 1869. The error was on page 74 of the fifth edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin.</hi></note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">CD and his family stayed at Caerdeon in North Wales from 12 June to 30 July 1869 (<ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1218.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Emma Darwin’s</ref> diary (DAR 242)).</note>
